Name: autosomal recessive hyaline body myopathy
Definition: A hyaline body myopathy that has_material_basis_in compound heterozygous or homozygous mutation in MYH7 on 14q11.2.

Name: autosomal dominant hyaline body myopathy
Definition: A hyaline body myopathy that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in MYH7 on 14q11.2.
